headline: 5 Infrastructure REITs Quietly Powering AI While Getting No Credit for It
summary: While Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) stock surged 34.9% over the past year and the S&P 500 gained 12.2%, the infrastructure REITs powering AI’s physical backbone have been left behind.
